#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:1
msgid "Database API"
msgstr "Database API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:3
msgid ""
"Database connection and query helpers are available under `ptool.db` and "
"`p.db`."
msgstr "数据库连接与查询辅助能力位于 `ptool.db` 和 `p.db` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:5
msgid "ptool.db.connect"
msgstr "ptool.db.connect"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:7
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:7"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:9
msgid ""
"`ptool.db.connect(url_or_options)` opens a database connection and returns a "
"`Connection` object."
msgstr "`ptool.db.connect(url_or_options)` 打开数据库连接，并返回一个 `Connection` 对"
"象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:12
msgid "Supported databases:"
msgstr "支持的数据库："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:14
msgid "SQLite"
msgstr "SQLite"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:15
msgid "PostgreSQL"
msgstr "PostgreSQL"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:16
msgid "MySQL"
msgstr "MySQL"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:18
msgid "Arguments:"
msgstr "参数："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:20
msgid "`url_or_options` (string|table, required):"
msgstr "`url_or_options`（string|table，必填）："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:20
msgid "When a string is provided, it is treated as the database URL."
msgstr "传入字符串时，会被视为数据库 URL。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:20
msgid "When a table is provided, it currently supports:"
msgstr "传入 table 时，目前支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:20
msgid "`url` (string, required): The database URL."
msgstr "`url`（string，必填）：数据库 URL。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:25
msgid "Supported URL examples:"
msgstr "支持的 URL 示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:33
msgid "SQLite notes:"
msgstr "SQLite 说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:35
msgid "`sqlite:test.db` and `sqlite://test.db` are supported."
msgstr "支持 `sqlite:test.db` 和 `sqlite://test.db`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:36
msgid ""
"Relative SQLite paths are resolved from the current `ptool` runtime "
"directory, so they follow `ptool.cd(...)`."
msgstr "相对 SQLite 路径会从当前 `ptool` 运行时目录解析，因此会受到 `ptool.cd(...)` "
"的影响。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:38
msgid ""
"If no `mode=` query parameter is provided, SQLite connections default to "
"`mode=rwc`, which allows creating the database file automatically."
msgstr "如果没有提供 `mode=` 查询参数，SQLite 连接默认使用 `mode=rwc`，从而允许自动 "
"创建数据库文件。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:41
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:41"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:50
msgid "Connection"
msgstr "Connection"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:52
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:52"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:54
msgid ""
"`Connection` represents an open database connection returned by "
"`ptool.db.connect()`."
msgstr "`Connection` 表示由 `ptool.db.connect()` 返回的已打开数据库连接。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:57
msgid "It is implemented as a Lua userdata."
msgstr "它实现为 Lua userdata。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:59
msgid "Methods:"
msgstr "方法："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:61
msgid "`db:query(sql, params?)` -> `table`"
msgstr "`db:query(sql, params?)` -> `table`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:62
msgid "`db:query_one(sql, params?)` -> `table|nil`"
msgstr "`db:query_one(sql, params?)` -> `table|nil`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:63
msgid "`db:scalar(sql, params?)` -> `boolean|integer|number|string|nil`"
msgstr "`db:scalar(sql, params?)` -> `boolean|integer|number|string|nil`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:64
msgid "`db:execute(sql, params?)` -> `table`"
msgstr "`db:execute(sql, params?)` -> `table`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:65
msgid "`db:transaction(fn)` -> `any`"
msgstr "`db:transaction(fn)` -> `any`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:66
msgid "`db:close()` -> `nil`"
msgstr "`db:close()` -> `nil`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:68
msgid "Parameter binding:"
msgstr "参数绑定："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:70
msgid "`params` is optional."
msgstr "`params` 可选。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:71
msgid ""
"When `params` is an array table, it is treated as positional parameters and "
"SQL placeholders should use `?`."
msgstr "当 `params` 是数组表时，会视为位置参数，SQL 占位符应使用 `?`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:73
msgid ""
"When `params` is a key-value table, it is treated as named parameters and "
"SQL placeholders should use `:name`."
msgstr "当 `params` 是键值表时，会视为命名参数，SQL 占位符应使用 `:name`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:75
msgid "Positional and named parameters cannot be mixed in the same call."
msgstr "同一次调用中不能混用位置参数和命名参数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:76
msgid "Supported parameter value types are:"
msgstr "支持的绑定值类型包括："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:76
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:76"
