msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:144"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:146
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.db.Connection:scalar`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.db.Connection:scalar`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:148
msgid ""
"`db:scalar(sql, params?)` returns the first column of the first row, or `nil`"
" if the query returns no rows."
msgstr "`db:scalar(sql, params?)` 返回第一行第一列的值，如果查询没有结果则返回 `nil`"
"。"

