msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:160"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:162
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.db.Connection:execute`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.db.Connection:execute`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:164
msgid ""
"`db:execute(sql, params?)` executes a statement and returns a table with:"
msgstr "`db:execute(sql, params?)` 执行语句，并返回一个包含以下字段的表："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:166
msgid "`rows_affected` (integer): The number of affected rows."
msgstr "`rows_affected`（integer）：受影响的行数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:168
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:168"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:175
msgid "transaction"
msgstr "transaction"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:177
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:177"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:179
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.db.Connection:transaction`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.db.Connection:transaction`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:181
msgid "`db:transaction(fn)` runs `fn(tx)` inside a database transaction."
msgstr "`db:transaction(fn)` 在数据库事务中执行 `fn(tx)`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:183
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:183"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:185
msgid "If `fn(tx)` returns normally, the transaction is committed."
msgstr "如果 `fn(tx)` 正常返回，则提交事务。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:186
msgid ""
"If `fn(tx)` raises an error, the transaction is rolled back and the error is "
"re-raised."
msgstr "如果 `fn(tx)` 抛错，则回滚事务并重新抛出错误。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:188
msgid "Nested transactions are not supported."
msgstr "不支持嵌套事务。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:189
msgid ""
"While the callback is active, the outer connection object must not be used; "
"use the provided `tx` object instead."
msgstr "在回调执行期间，不得使用外层连接对象；应改用传入的 `tx` 对象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:192
msgid "The `tx` object supports the same query methods as `Connection`:"
msgstr "`tx` 对象支持与 `Connection` 相同的查询方法："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:194
msgid "`tx:query(sql, params?)`"
msgstr "`tx:query(sql, params?)`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:195
msgid "`tx:query_one(sql, params?)`"
msgstr "`tx:query_one(sql, params?)`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:196
msgid "`tx:scalar(sql, params?)`"
msgstr "`tx:scalar(sql, params?)`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:197
msgid "`tx:execute(sql, params?)`"
msgstr "`tx:execute(sql, params?)`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:199
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:199"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:217
msgid "close"
msgstr "close"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:219
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:219"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:221
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.db.Connection:close`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.db.Connection:close`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:223
msgid "`db:close()` closes the connection."
msgstr "`db:close()` 关闭连接。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:225
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:225"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:227
msgid "After closing, the connection can no longer be used."
msgstr "关闭后，连接不能再继续使用。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/db.md:228
msgid "Closing during an active transaction callback raises an error."
